bot.defaultPrefix: Default prefix of the bot (DEPRECIED: Discord uses slash commands now)

settingsDbl.id: ID of the Discord webhook (to show a message when someone voted for the bot)
settingsDbl.token: Token of the Discord webhook (to show a message when someone voted for the bot)

mspLogin.username: Username of the MSP accounts (must be identical for all servers)
mspLogin.password: Password of the MSP accounts (must be identical for all servers)

join.id: ID of Discord webhook (to show a message when someone invited the bot in a server)
join.token: Token of Discord webhook (to show a message when someone invited the bot in a server)

leave.id: ID of Discord webhook (to show a message when someone kicked the bot in a server)
leave.token: Token of Discord webhook (to show a message when someone kicked the bot in a server)

shards.id: ID of Discord webhook (to show a message when the status of a shard is updated)
shards.token: Token of Discord webhook (to show a message when the status of a shard is updated)

settingsWebhook.id: ID of Discord webhook (to show a message when someone did a command)
settingsWebhook.token: Token of Discord webhook (to show a message when someone did a command)

warningHistogram.id: ID of Discord webhook (to show a warning message when a histogram needs to be built)
warningHistogram.token: Token of Discord webhook (to show a warning message when a histogram needs to be built)
